<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-silly-stupid">1.★ <strong>愚蠢的；可笑的 (silly / stupid)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's foolish of you to waste your time like this.
